WEBVTT

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:08.787
Hey, good morning family. I'm excited to be with you all today. I really truly am. We want to start a new channel.

00:00:08.788 --> 00:00:27.118
I feel in my heart—I have a lot of people that have wanted to sponsor and do things with this channel, but the Lord told me never allow people who were trying to sell a product to be on this channel.

00:00:27.119 --> 00:00:37.569
Now, I thought about putting anointing oils and things like that because you asked for it—anything that has to do with the church, but nothing like t-shirts and things like that. Does that make sense?

00:00:37.570 --> 00:00:54.279
I've dedicated this channel to the Father so that He has an avenue to speak to His people, whether He wants to speak through me or if He gives me a word through somebody else—like those last two words that lined up with what He gave me prophetically already.

00:00:54.280 --> 00:00:59.619
So, we've been praying, and my wife is really good at doing eBay.

00:00:59.620 --> 00:01:06.472
We're starting a channel and just announcing it now. If you want to follow it, fine. If you don't, fine. But we're going to be doing a channel.

00:01:06.473 --> 00:01:13.670
It's a blog channel, an everyday channel, as much as my wife is able to because she homeschools the kids and stuff.

00:01:13.671 --> 00:01:20.529
It's a lot of work homeschooling and doing all the things we do because we have a teenager, Braden.

00:01:20.530 --> 00:01:32.085
The channel's name is Come Thrift with Me. Our goal for 2024 is teaching people how to do a side hustle.

00:01:32.086 --> 00:01:36.122
There's a lot of people I see who are struggling financially.

00:01:36.123 --> 00:01:42.810
I'm not saying I have it all together, y'all, but I trust God and I believe for everything I have.

00:01:42.811 --> 00:01:47.314
And He has provided a lot through Poshmark and through eBay.

00:01:47.315 --> 00:01:53.516
He gives me places; He'll tell me where to go find the merchandise, the t-shirts, the shoes, or whatever.

00:01:53.517 --> 00:02:00.034
I pray in the car. I ask God, 'Show me where do we go today, Father,'and I'm going to do that. I'm going to film it.

00:02:00.035 --> 00:02:11.439
I want to show you all how I use the prophetic gifting that God's given me—seeing and knowing—and how I use it to apply to everyday life.

00:02:11.440 --> 00:02:20.175
People think it's always hyper-spiritual, but I'm just a real person who has real needs and needs bills met every single day.

00:02:20.176 --> 00:02:33.156
Just like everyone, once a month, you pay your electric, water, gas, your mortgage, and your car payment; you've got to pay for that stuff unless you're debt-free, which some people are, but most of us aren't.

00:02:33.157 --> 00:02:36.639
And so, we have to believe for food. We have to believe for things.

00:02:36.640 --> 00:02:41.149
So, I'm going to show you all that side if you want to watch it.

00:02:41.150 --> 00:02:45.430
Some people might not care; they just want to hear the prophetic words and move on.

00:02:45.431 --> 00:03:04.268
But some people want to hear how to list on eBay, how my wife does inventory, and creative ideas to get extra wealth—doing things like thrifting, showing you what to buy, what not to buy, and what will sell for extra money.

00:03:04.269 --> 00:03:08.689
If you're interested in that and you want to come to our new channel, cool.

00:03:08.690 --> 00:03:18.345
The other part of it was the Lord put it on my heart to show you—I thought about making it fun—doing things I like, as I'm a gun enthusiast.

00:03:18.346 --> 00:03:34.060
I like guns and shooting and being out on the ranch with my dad and showing the Longhorn cattle and riding on the gator, going fishing, popping fireworks, or whatever.

00:03:34.061 --> 00:03:40.645
We have a place where we pop fireworks and camp, doing survival stuff.

00:03:40.646 --> 00:03:56.270
I'll show you what to do with your relatives that are left behind, leaving things for them, and showing you silver coins to barter with—which I feel in my spirit.

00:03:56.271 --> 00:04:02.145
Now, some of you may want to argue about it, and that's fine, but I'm telling you, I believe we're going to see some things ahead.

00:04:02.146 --> 00:04:17.693
I believe with all my heart you need bartering things: bartering food, silver, or maybe some gold little Krugerrands.

00:04:17.694 --> 00:04:31.544
I just have ideas the Lord has given me for a blog. I also wanted to update you on my weight loss. I've been praying.

00:04:31.545 --> 00:04:49.725
There were so many different ideas about what we should be eating: the carnivore diet, the keto diet, Mediterranean keto, all these different things.

00:04:49.726 --> 00:04:57.580
The first part of January, detoxing from all the sugar I used to consume was brutal.

00:04:57.581 --> 00:05:01.971
I thought I wasn't going to make it through this, but the Lord kept saying, 'You don't have a choice.

00:05:01.972 --> 00:05:08.979
You've got to do this.'So I went into prayer and fasting, started doing intermittent fasting, and started interceding.

00:05:08.980 --> 00:05:13.532
One day, the Lord spoke to me—I think it was around January 10th.

00:05:13.533 --> 00:05:18.632
He said to me, because I said, 'Lord, I'm doing carnivore and I'm not losing anything.

00:05:18.633 --> 00:05:30.634
What's going on?'I was eating a ton of meat all day long—steak, chicken—I would eat huge plates of meat.

00:05:30.635 --> 00:05:36.350
And the Lord spoke to me and said, 'Brandon, it's about calories.

00:05:36.351 --> 00:05:46.646
You're eating way too much.'He said, 'Your body, even if you're on the carnivore diet, cannot burn off all the food that you're consuming.

00:05:46.647 --> 00:06:04.928
So, you need to go back to monitoring how many calories you are consuming on a day-to-day basis.'I started adding up how much steak, chicken, turkey, and meat I was eating, and I realized I was eating a ton of calories.

00:06:04.929 --> 00:06:09.810
That's why I wasn't losing weight; my body couldn't burn it all off.

00:06:09.811 --> 00:06:18.503
When it's as cold as it has been, I haven't been able to exercise outside, so of course you're not going to lose weight when consuming so much food.

00:06:18.504 --> 00:06:36.134
The Lord said, 'I want you to monitor every single day how many calories you are consuming.'So, I started keeping underneath 1,800 calories.

00:06:36.135 --> 00:06:48.129
My wife, my little researcher, found an app that is phenomenal.

00:06:48.130 --> 00:06:51.242
It monitors your calories and tells you what you're eating.

00:06:51.243 --> 00:07:01.095
You can type in the restaurant, and it shows you exactly what's in it, along with your exercise and how many glasses of water you need every day.

00:07:01.096 --> 00:07:14.799
I think it was about 20 dollars apiece. She's doing it with me to help motivate me and we're doing it together.

00:07:14.800 --> 00:07:29.298
She doesn't need to lose any weight, but she's such a blessing helping me log all the drinks and everything I do in a day.

00:07:29.299 --> 00:07:43.138
Keeping on track, I've lost 14 pounds in the last three weeks. To God be the glory; I'm going in the right direction.

00:07:43.139 --> 00:07:54.220
It's not always been easy, but I'm drinking my diet shake and logging it.

00:07:54.221 --> 00:08:10.553
Instead of what I used to have for a snack, I'm just trying to find ways to make this a journey that's going to last forever, instead of something like a fad diet that I get burned out on as I have in the past.

00:08:10.554 --> 00:08:18.588
You lose a lot of weight and then you gain it all back. I said, 'God, show me how to make this a lifestyle.

00:08:18.589 --> 00:08:34.793
Help me.'I know a lot of people struggle with lifestyle changes that lead to yo-yo dieting, where you lose 100 pounds like I'm after and then gain it all back.

00:08:34.794 --> 00:08:49.434
My goal is to have all of my weight off before October. The app even shows you that if you maintain these calories every single day, seven days a week, you will be at that weight by October.

00:08:49.435 --> 00:08:55.420
So, I thought it was really cool. So, I'm like, let's try it. I'm down 14 pounds.

00:08:55.421 --> 00:09:01.037
So, I just wanted to update y'all on the weight loss and where I'm at with it. I told you I would.

00:09:01.038 --> 00:09:06.026
I didn't want to make it boring by coming out and telling you every single week.

00:09:06.027 --> 00:09:10.025
But maybe I'll put that on the blog channel—the other channel I told y'all about.

00:09:10.026 --> 00:09:19.260
The channels that we're starting, "Come Thrift With Me,"will be about prepping, thrifting, guns, and the fun things.

00:09:19.261 --> 00:09:27.708
Like I said, most people don't agree with carrying guns. Most people don't want to talk about them. Whatever.

00:09:27.709 --> 00:09:34.159
I personally carry a firearm with me wherever I go in this day and age with all these people acting crazy.

00:09:34.160 --> 00:09:42.055
People say, "Well, you should use Psalm 91."I use both. I use Psalm 91 and I carry a sword at the same time.

00:09:42.056 --> 00:09:45.639
I make sure my wife and my children are protected at all costs.

00:09:45.640 --> 00:09:50.347
You know, I believe in my angels, but I also believe in the Second Amendment.

00:09:50.348 --> 00:09:54.310
And most people may not like that, but that's fine. That's between you and God.

00:09:54.311 --> 00:09:59.367
For me, I'm a Southerner. We live in the South, and I was raised with guns my whole life.

00:09:59.368 --> 00:10:03.119
My dad—this is the way our hunters were. We're fishers. We hunt.

00:10:03.120 --> 00:10:12.113
We fish. We do it all. That's just the way we are. And so most people don't like that, but you'll get over it.

00:10:12.114 --> 00:10:20.559
I mean, that's just the way it is. You know, we believe we have a right to defend ourselves and protect our families.

00:10:20.560 --> 00:10:28.719
And so, I'll show you about guns and things like that in another channel and about thrifting.

00:10:28.720 --> 00:10:38.159
It'll be a fun variety of stuff to watch. I want to keep this about prayer over here on this platform.

00:10:38.160 --> 00:10:43.811
If you want to stay, you can stay over here. It's going to be about prayer, intercessory prayer. It's going to be about the prophetic.

00:10:43.812 --> 00:10:50.908
It's going to be about everything the Lord gives me, bringing things and talking to you just like it is right now.

00:10:50.909 --> 00:11:06.180
But I just felt like I would add some other things because I'm telling you, through the spring, through the summer, going into the fall, there's going to become great suppression over freedom of speech a lot on these platforms.

00:11:06.181 --> 00:11:27.998
So, if I was to all of a sudden disappear from this channel, you would know where to find me because I don't know how much longer I can talk freely the way I do like this for what I have seen coming with religious persecution and suppression.

00:11:27.999 --> 00:11:35.278
Does that make sense? Because we are entering into a different time like we've never seen before.

00:11:35.279 --> 00:11:51.683
So if you can't find me and this channel's gone, I'll be on the other one and I probably won't come out as bold over there, but at least you know where I am until I can get something more set up so I didn't just disappear.

00:11:51.684 --> 00:12:00.216
I'm still around. My wife just said we don't have any videos over there yet, but I'm making them and I'm fixing to make it right after this.

00:12:00.217 --> 00:12:10.114
I have an idea and I'm trying to make it fun. And no, we're not going anyplace. No, I'm not shutting this down. I just want you to hear that.

00:12:10.115 --> 00:12:19.518
I'm just trying to do something different on top of it because of what I feel is coming.

00:12:19.519 --> 00:12:25.674
I hear way in advance, y'all. I try not to freak everybody out, but the Lord does talk to me.

00:12:25.675 --> 00:12:30.632
You'll know. The more you get to know me, you'll know. So, okay, there you go.

00:12:30.633 --> 00:12:39.556
Father, I just thank you, Lord, for every single person that is represented here. I plead the blood of Jesus over every family.

00:12:39.557 --> 00:12:54.244
I thank you, Father, for the gifts and for the surprises, the finding money, the bills paid off, the blessing and increase, the blessings on these people, that there is a supernatural turn of events coming to their homes.

00:12:54.245 --> 00:12:58.976
Father, they come over and help with the other channel and watch how you've blessed me.

00:12:58.977 --> 00:13:05.177
Lord, I promise to give you all the glory and all the praise for everything you've ever given me.

00:13:05.178 --> 00:13:11.560
Father, it's never me; it's always you. Father, I want to be at the spout where the glory comes about.

00:13:11.561 --> 00:13:17.784
And Father, that the light would shine on our faces, that we would show your glory.

00:13:17.785 --> 00:13:29.199
And that, Father, that people would see the manifested presence on our life and that they would want it and they would see it and we would lead them to you because it's always about you.

00:13:29.200 --> 00:13:39.091
It's nothing about us. Father, I thank you, Lord, that we do die daily to ourselves, but Father in that, we take up the cross and we follow you.

00:13:39.092 --> 00:13:45.799
I thank you, Lord, that we become more like you, less of the world and more like Jesus every day.

00:13:45.800 --> 00:13:51.439
Father, I thank you, Lord, for every single person on here. Every need that they have is met.

00:13:51.440 --> 00:13:58.512
That they have that hunger to come after you with all their hearts, minds, souls, and strength.

00:13:58.513 --> 00:14:06.914
And I thank you, Father, that a supernatural increase is coming over their marriages, over their children, over their schooling.

