A covering—no weapon formed against them would prosper. We cover a covering of blood around and about them in the name of Jesus.

00:14:14.227 --> 00:14:24.876
We thank you, Lord, that no weapon formed against them will prosper from every area of their life and every tongue that rises against them, we condemn it.

00:14:24.877 --> 00:14:33.089
Every word curse, every satanic witchcraft, all voodoo, spells, incantations, whatever, it does not matter.

00:14:33.090 --> 00:14:47.127
It falls at the feet and we plead the blood over us. Every tongue that rises against us, we condemn those words and they fall to the ground. You will not bear fruit in our lives at all.

