We plead the blood over every one of us, our children right now and over my wife and over our home.

00:15:05.294 --> 00:15:12.397
We thank you, Lord, for your angels that protect us and they bear us up in their hands lest we dash our foot against a stone.

00:15:12.398 --> 00:15:22.262
We bind the spirit of strife out of this house. We bind any kind of demonic spirit that would try to come in and cause havoc in our home.

00:15:22.263 --> 00:15:29.692
We plead the blood of Jesus all around us. Father, we thank you, Lord, that we're protected.

00:15:29.693 --> 00:15:39.665
From the top of our head to the soles of our feet, from the top of our car bumper to the back, all the way around the sides, we're covered with angels.

