You said we have the helmet of salvation. We have the sword of the spirit.

00:15:55.483 --> 00:16:00.363
We have the shield of faith. We quench all the fiery darts of the wicked.

00:16:00.364 --> 00:16:06.976
We thank you, Lord, that we're not afraid of the terror of the night, nor for the arrow that flieth by day. We're not afraid.

00:16:06.977 --> 00:16:17.623
And we call Psalm 91 and Psalm 23 over our homes, that you protect us and you guide us and you have a plan for our life.

00:16:17.624 --> 00:16:28.319
Father, I thank you, Lord, that your word says that your beloved—I wish above all things you prosper and be in health even as your soul prospers.

