And we use the love of God to cast out that fear because my Father loves me and he loves you and he doesn't want you to walk in fear.

00:17:08.250 --> 00:17:16.270
And Father, we thank you, Lord, that love is made perfect in us, that we realize how much you love us. You're a good God. You're faithful.

00:17:16.271 --> 00:17:25.313
And we thank you, Lord, for your hedge of blood and protection around about us at all times in these last days.

00:17:25.314 --> 00:17:32.425
Lord, we thank you that you come quickly for us. You come quickly, Lord.

00:17:32.426 --> 00:17:38.975
